    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220&deg;C/ 200&deg;C (fan)/ 425&deg;F/ Gas 7</p> <p>Add the <strong>basmati rice</strong> and 300ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> to a pot with a lid and bring to the boil over a high heat</p> <p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 10-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p> <p>Once cooked, remove from the heat and keep covered until serving</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chipotle-fish-green-rice-and-cucumber-salsa/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>basa fillets</strong> to a lightly oiled baking tray&nbsp;</p> <p>Spread the&nbsp;the <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (Can't handle the heat? Go easy!) over the<strong> basa&nbsp;</strong>and season with a pinch of salt</p> <p>Put the tray in the oven for 8-10 min or until cooked through&nbsp;</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chipotle-fish-green-rice-and-cucumber-salsa/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p> <p>Add the <strong>chopped coriander</strong> to a pestle and mortar with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong></p> <p>Grind the <strong>coriander</strong> to a fine paste and set aside&nbsp;</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chipotle-fish-green-rice-and-cucumber-salsa/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>cucumber</strong> in half and scrape out the inner seeds with a teaspoon, throw the watery seeds away</p> <p>Grate the <strong>cucumber&nbsp;</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chipotle-fish-green-rice-and-cucumber-salsa/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Chop the<strong> cherry tomatoes</strong> roughly into small pieces&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chipotle-fish-green-rice-and-cucumber-salsa/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped cherry tomatoes </strong>and<strong> cucumber</strong>&nbsp;to a bowl</p> <p>Add the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span><strong> lime</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>&nbsp;<span class=\"text-highlight\">&ndash;</span> this is your <strong>cucumber &amp; tomato salsa</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chipotle-fish-green-rice-and-cucumber-salsa/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>rice</strong> is cooked, fluff it with a fork and stir through the <strong>coriander paste</strong></p> <p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>&nbsp;<span class=\"text-highlight\">&ndash;</span> this is your <strong>green rice&nbsp;</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chipotle-fish-green-rice-and-cucumber-salsa/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Cut the remaining <strong>lime</strong> into wedges</p> <p>Serve the<strong> cooked fish</strong> over the <strong>green rice</strong> with the <strong>cucumber &amp; tomato salsa</strong> to the side</p> <p>Garnish with a wedge of<strong> lime</strong></p> <p>Enjoy!&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
